0.130 0.150 0.190 rg BT /F1 11.20 Tf 58.00 586.98 Td (OWASP Dependency-Check is a software composition analysis tool. Its main job is to) Tj ET
0.130 0.150 0.190 rg BT /F1 11.20 Tf 58.00 569.95 Td (inspect the third-party components used by an application and determine whether those) Tj ET
0.130 0.150 0.190 rg BT /F1 11.20 Tf 58.00 552.93 Td (components are associated with known vulnerabilities.) Tj ET
0.130 0.150 0.190 rg BT /F1 11.20 Tf 58.00 527.90 Td (It focuses on the dependency layer rather than the application's own custom logic.) Tj ET
0.130 0.150 0.190 rg BT /F1 11.20 Tf 58.00 510.88 Td (That makes it different from SonarQube and complementary to it.) Tj ET
0.130 0.150 0.190 rg BT /F1 11.20 Tf 58.00 485.86 Td (A simple way to think about it is:) Tj ET
0.130 0.150 0.190 rg BT /F1 11.20 Tf 82.00 461.06 Td (SonarQube asks whether your own code contains risky patterns or poor-quality) Tj ET
