0.130 0.150 0.190 rg BT /F1 11.20 Tf 82.00 425.46 Td (Dependency-Check asks whether the libraries, packages, or bundled components) Tj ET
0.880 0.600 0.200 rg 64.00 429.46 6.00 6.00 re f
0.130 0.150 0.190 rg BT /F1 11.20 Tf 82.00 408.66 Td (you depend on are already known to be vulnerable.) Tj ET
0.130 0.150 0.190 rg BT /F1 11.20 Tf 58.00 389.63 Td (This is important because modern applications often contain far more third-party code) Tj ET
0.130 0.150 0.190 rg BT /F1 11.20 Tf 58.00 372.61 Td (than first-party code.) Tj ET
